https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323632034/image_1323632034.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">Ford Mustang Mach-E all-electric SUV</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jax10289</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Ford Motor Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/F\" title=\"Ford Motor Company\">F</a></span>) and other incumbent automakers heavily invested in battery-electric vehicle (BEV) technology have been scrambling to contend with consumers\u2019 lukewarm acceptance of their new models.</p> <p>As of 2022, Ford vowed to invest $50 billion on BEVs. The automaker has</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323632034/image_1323632034.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743120-ford-facing-battery-electric-roadblocks-time-to-consider-byd", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 01:09:30"}, {"id": "4743117", "title": "Star Bulk Carriers: 3 Reasons To Consider An Investment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1372933783/image_1372933783.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nautical Vessel (Bulk Carrier Ship) sailing at Detroit Canal at Night\" data-id=\"1372933783\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1372933783/image_1372933783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1372933783/image_1372933783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1372933783/image_1372933783.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/