1879228542\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BING-JHEN HONG</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In this article, I will provide an overview of <b>Nvidia Corporation</b> (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" class=\"ticker-link\">NVDA</a>) earnings of Q3 25, which were <a href=\"https://s201.q4cdn.com/141608511/files/doc_financials/2025/q3/ed2a395c-5e9b-4411-8b4a-a718d192155a.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">released a couple of weeks ago</a>, on November 20<sup>th</sup>, 2024. Plus, I will express my view</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1879228542/image_1879228542.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743115-nvidia-q3-ai-dominance-strong-growth-make-it-a-strong-buy-for-the-future", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 00:42:24"}, {"id": "4743114", "title": "DGRS: Good Fundamentals, But Subpar Dividend Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Small Cap write on sticky notes isolated on Office Desk. Stock market concept\" data-id=\"1283342758\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">syahrir maulana</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article updates <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4630314-dgrs-finding-dividend-growth-in-small-caps\">my latest review on DGRS</a>, in light of its current portfolio and recent performance.</p> <h3><strong>DGRS strategy</strong></h3> <p>WisdomTree U.S. SmallCap Quality Dividend Growth Fund (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DGRS\" title=\"WisdomTree U.S. SmallCap Quality Dividend Growth Fund ETF\">DGRS</a></span>) was launched on 07/25/2013 and tracks the WisdomTree U.S. SmallCap</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1283342758/image_1283342758.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743114-dgrs-good-fundamentals-but-subpar-dividend-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 00:21:18"}, {"id": "4743113", "title": "Realty Income: Turning Bullish For Once", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Large 7-11 Convenience Building Store with customer service parking lot area against blue sky background at Samut Sakhon, Thailand - March 31, 2023\" data-id=\"1499955814\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"958px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499955814/image_1499955814.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes